LICENSE — ipax-cli
==================

This tool depends on @ipax/core, which contains code derived from IPAX 2
by Santiago Bustelo (https://bustelo.com.ar), used with the author's
permission under CC-BY attribution terms (permission granted 2026-06-10).

Attribution: Santiago Bustelo is credited by name with links in this
repository. This is consistent with the CC-BY license direction the
author intends to adopt for IPAX.

@ipax/core also depends on the APCA contrast algorithm (apca-w3.js),
copyright © 2019-2022 Andrew Somers / Myndex Research, used under the
W3 license for web content accessibility purposes.

The original portions of this project (index.js, parse-color.js,
ipax-find.js, ipax-palette.js, ipax-stack.js, mcp-server.js) are the
work of the contributors listed in the git history.

See NOTICE for full attribution details.
